iting the selected restaurant and then navigating.`; ``HomeScreen.kt` composes the top profile affordance, content sections, and bottom-shell relationship used by the shared navigation surface.`; ``HomeScreen.kt` observes `HomeViewModel` state so ads, categories, favourites, and restaurants recompose immediately as backing data changes.`; ``HomeScreen.kt` does not request runtime permissions.`; ``HomeScreen.kt` reads view-model state on entry and updates system bars while composing the feed.`; ``HomeViewModel.kt` aggregates repository-backed ads, food items, restaurants, and liked restaurants into observable screen state.`; ``HomeViewModel.kt` aggregates repository state and does not request runtime permissions.`; ``HomeViewModel.kt` loads repository-backed lists during initialization so the home feed is ready when the screen appears.`; ``AdCard.kt` renders a bundled ad illustration inside the home carousel card.`\n72: - risk hints: `current-phase source features are still open`; `critical/high behavior cannot close on build pass alone`; `broad shell endpoint risk`; `related platform capability must be resolved with Cangjie-callable API, replacement, fallback blocker, or deferred evidence`\n73: - acceptance evidence: `Closed critical/high features must record sourceBehavior, targetBehavior, parityLevel, targetEndpoints, and verificationEvidence.`; `Build pass alone is not per-feature verification.`; `Referenced target tests need to be covered by the latest accepted test gate or explicit verificationEvidence.`; `Related platform capabilities must cite targetCapabilitySearch and a Cangjie-callable API, verified replacement, fallback blocker, or deferred blocker.`; `Replace root/shell/whole-file endpoints with precise target functions, types, resource files, or tests before closure.`\n74: - test hints: `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase04_home_history_discovery_test.cj::homeStoreLoadsFixtureBackedSections (PASS 2026-06-28)`; `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase04_home_history_disc